{"tid":1528640,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[小心]行屋邨開遮/行sim蓬","createTime":"2019-09-01T14:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T14:56:24.000Z","uid":310029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4db5a9ed0f03e996a5e4dd702d38ebf35388cab6","tid":1528640,"uid":310029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:39:35.000Z","msg":"（無圖sor9）事緣係咁,琴晚大圍搞左次百人size屋邨巡遊<br />\n<br />\n本身行經新翠、隆亨、雲疊都相安無事,仲越行越多手足加入<br />\n<br />\n點知行到美林就有廢老係高空掉垃圾落黎<br />\n<br />\n咁都算,我地捉唔到人就散左<br />\n<br />\n及後我留左係美楓樓下同個藍絲伯伯理性討論緊,點鳩知就有人係樓上掉兩個玻璃樽落黎,差D就滅鳩左我口<br />\n<br />\n非散佈黑色恐怖,但手足們下次入邨真係要擔遮/行sim蓬,要留命抗爭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw今日係青馬收費站塞死,入唔到機場陪大家sor呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4124b22ec01e44736a2fac15da8a911d3340cc16","tid":1528640,"uid":304456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:42:52.000Z","msg":"屋村係甘衰   勁多痴線佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caeae21f2c7caa90b0c97b6b13101c2d22231978","tid":1528640,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:56:24.000Z","msg":"屋邨本身都有高空擲物<br />\n更何況以家藍絲暴力升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之小心"}]}